title.narrative: COMMUNICATIONS, ADVOCACY AND PARTNERSHIP ON CHILDREN S RIGHTS

description.narrative: UNICEF staff and partners are provided tools, guidance and resources to improve communications and advocate for and establish partnerships on children's rights issues., which contributes to Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas, Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas (Covid), Private Sector Engagement. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Developing And Leveraging Resources And Partnerships, Fostering Innovation And Use Of New Technologies, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: The country programme is effectively coordinated, managed and supported to achieve results for children
